column2: select SpecPhotoAll.objID, SpecPhotoAll.plate as SDSSplate, SpecPhotoAll.mjd as SDSSmjd, SpecPhotoAll.fiberID, SpecPhotoAll.ra as SDSSra, SpecPhotoAll.dec as SDSSdec, XX_new.* into mydb.giantIDs_new3 from DR9.SpecPhotoAll, mydb.XX_new where SpecPhotoAll.plate = XX_new.plate and SpecPhotoAll.mjd = XX_new.mjd and SpecPhotoAll.fiberID = XX_new.fib
